title.rendered: Strapit Professional Stretch Underwrap Fixit Tape 5cm x 10m

content.rendered:
This is the very best hypoallergenic underwrap tape on the market. Combining a strong adhesive specifically designed for sport and being latex-free, this is one of our most popular products.

Non-woven hypoallergenic fabric tape

Latex-free adhesive

Subtle longitudinal and transverse stretch

Ideal for pre-taping of knees, shoulders and other joints

Ideal for sensitive or regular tape application

excerpt.rendered:
